communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Calendars for the following officials over the past six months:

Joel Engardio
Myrna Melgar
London Breed 

Any and all communications between the following persons:

Mayor London Breed

Zach Rosen

Robin Pam

Todd David 

Eddie Kim

Myrna Melgar

Any and all communications between those persons that mention Mayor London Breed, Zach Rosen, Robin Pam, Todd David, Joel Engardio, Myrna Melgar, and Eddie Kim that mention The Great Highway, Friends of Great Highway Park, Great Highway Park, Gazetteer.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Belle Reve

title: UNREDACTED emails request from London Breed

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

I requested all communications between London Breed and those involved with the Yes on Prop. K initiative. I received the attached 11-page document containing emails in which ALL information is redacted. I  demanding a fully UNREDACTED document. 

They exceeded their time to turn over these documents so I request immediate action on your part.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Belle Reve
